---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
const lastUpdated = '2026-06-29'
---
<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Super Calculator"
  description="Privacy Policy for SuperCalculator.xyz. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your information."
  canonical="https://supercalculator.xyz/privacy"
  lastUpdated={lastUpdated}
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <nav class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-6 flex gap-1 items-center">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-blue-600">Home</a><span>›</span>
      <span class="text-gray-900">Privacy Policy</span>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-10">Effective date: June 29, 2026 · Last updated: June 29, 2026</p>

    <div class="prose-content space-y-8 text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>Welcome to <strong>Super Calculator</strong> ("we," "us," or "our"), operated at <strong>supercalculator.xyz</strong>. We are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and your rights regarding that information.</p>
        <p class="mt-2">By using supercalculator.xyz, you agree to the practices described in this policy. If you do not agree, please do not use the site.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">2. Information We Do Not Collect</h2>
        <p>All calculations on Super Calculator run <strong>entirely in your browser</strong>. No calculation inputs, results, or personal financial or health data are transmitted to our servers or stored anywhere. We do not collect:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Mortgage amounts, loan figures, or financial inputs you enter</li>
          <li>Health data such as weight, height, or BMI inputs</li>
          <li>Any calculation results you generate</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">3. Information We May Collect Automatically</h2>
        <p>When you visit supercalculator.xyz, we may automatically receive limited technical information, including:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Log data:</strong> Your IP address, browser type, operating system, referring URL, pages visited, and time of visit</li>
          <li><strong>Device information:</strong> Device type and screen resolution</li>
          <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> Small files stored on your device for site functionality and analytics (see Section 6)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">This information is used solely to operate, maintain, and improve the website.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">4. Information You Voluntarily Provide</h2>
        <p>If you contact us via our Contact page, you provide your name, email address, and message. We use this information only to respond to your inquiry. We do not sell, rent, or share this information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">5. How We Use Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Provide and improve the Super Calculator service</li>
          <li>Analyze how the site is used in aggregate (no personal profiling)</li>
          <li>Detect and prevent technical issues or abuse</li>
          <li>Respond to contact form inquiries</li>
          <li>Comply with applicable legal obligations</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">6. Cookies and Analytics</h2>
        <p>We may use cookies and similar tracking technologies to understand how visitors use the site. We may use third-party analytics services such as <strong>Google Analytics</strong>, which collect anonymized usage data. Google Analytics may set its own cookies. You can opt out via <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Google's opt-out tool</a>.</p>
        <p class="mt-2">You can disable cookies in your browser settings. Disabling cookies will not affect your ability to use our calculators.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">7. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We may use the following third-party services, each with their own privacy policies:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — CDN, DNS, and DDoS protection. Cloudflare may process traffic data as a network intermediary.</li>
          <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> — anonymized usage analytics</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">We do not sell your data to advertisers or data brokers.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">8. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>Super Calculator does not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe a child under 13 has provided us personal information, please contact us and we will delete it promptly.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">9. Your Rights (California & U.S. State Law)</h2>
        <p>Depending on your state of residence, you may have rights under applicable U.S. privacy laws including the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA) and similar state laws:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Right to know</strong> what personal data we have collected about you</li>
          <li><strong>Right to delete</strong> personal data we hold</li>
          <li><strong>Right to opt out</strong> of the sale of personal data (we do not sell personal data)</li>
          <li><strong>Right to non-discrimination</strong> for exercising your privacy rights</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:aifi2k02@gmail.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">aifi2k02@gmail.com</a>.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">10. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We implement reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect information from unauthorized access, loss, or misuse. However, no internet transmission is 100% secure. Use the site at your own risk.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">11. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>Contact form submissions are retained only as long as necessary to respond to your inquiry, and no longer than 12 months. Anonymized analytics data may be retained longer for aggregate analysis.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">12. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes your acceptance of the revised policy.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">13. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at:</p>
        <div class="mt-3 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg px-5 py-4">
          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Super Calculator</p>
          <p>Website: <a href="https://supercalculator.xyz" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">supercalculator.xyz</a></p>
          <p>Email: <a href="mailto:aifi2k02@gmail.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">aifi2k02@gmail.com</a></p>
        </div>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
